    <item>
      <title>Pimco 预计日本央行最快将于 3 月份开始多次加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/pimco-sees-multiple-boj-rate-hikes-starting-as-soon-as-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[太平洋投资管理公司(Pacific Investment Management Co.)表示，日本央行可能最早在3月份取消负利率政策，并在今年多次加息，这将加剧该国政府债券的悲观前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/pimco-sees-multiple-boj-rate-hikes-starting-as-soon-as-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市涨势延续，投资者等待更多政策支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/china-stock-rally-extends-as-policy-support-optimism-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市周三继续上涨，这表明投资者越来越希望当局采取更有力的措施来维持刚刚开始的市场复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/china-stock-rally-extends-as-policy-support-optimism-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 01:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
